---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="Miss Moley's 30th — Bordeaux | The Void"
	description="A birthday trip agenda for a weekend in Bordeaux — 30th July to 2nd August."
>
	<div class="b30-page">
		<!-- ============================================================
		     HERO / COVER
		     ============================================================ -->
		<section class="hero-cover" aria-label="Cover">
			<a href="/" class="back-link" aria-label="Back to home">&larr; back</a>

			<!-- Large "30" watermark behind content -->
			<span class="hero-watermark" aria-hidden="true">30</span>

			<!-- Wine glass motif -->
			<div class="hero-motif" aria-hidden="true">
				<svg
					viewBox="0 0 120 200"
					xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
					class="hero-motif-svg"
				>
					<!-- Bowl — open at the rim, two separate strokes -->
					<path
						d="M 35 30 Q 30 70, 42 95 Q 50 108, 60 112"
						fill="none"
						stroke="currentColor"
						stroke-width="1.2"
						stroke-linecap="round"
						opacity="0.55"></path>
					<path
						d="M 85 30 Q 90 70, 78 95 Q 70 108, 60 112"
						fill="none"
						stroke="currentColor"
						stroke-width="1.2"
						stroke-linecap="round"
						opacity="0.55"></path>
					<!-- Rim -->
					<ellipse
						cx="60"
						cy="30"
						rx="25"
						ry="5"
						fill="none"
						stroke="currentColor"
						stroke-width="0.8"
						opacity="0.35"></ellipse>
					<!-- Wine surface -->
					<ellipse
						cx="60"
						cy="55"
						rx="19"
						ry="4"
						fill="none"
						stroke="currentColor"
						stroke-width="0.8"
						opacity="0.3"></ellipse>
					<!-- Wine fill -->
					<path
						class="wine-fill-path"
						d="M 41 55 Q 60 61, 79 55 Q 85 75, 60 106 Q 35 75, 41 55"
						fill="currentColor"
						opacity="0.18"></path>
					<!-- Stem -->
					<line
						x1="60"
						y1="112"
						x2="60"
						y2="165"
						stroke="currentColor"
						stroke-width="1.2"
						stroke-linecap="round"
						opacity="0.55"></line>
					<!-- Base -->
					<path
						d="M 40 165 Q 60 170, 80 165"
						fill="none"
						stroke="currentColor"
						stroke-width="1.2"
						stroke-linecap="round"
						opacity="0.55"></path>
				</svg>
			</div>

			<div class="hero-content">
				<span class="hero-label">A Birthday Trip</span>
				<h1 class="hero-title">Miss Moley's 30th</h1>
				<div class="hero-divider" aria-hidden="true"></div>
				<p class="hero-subtitle">Agenda</p>
				<p class="hero-dates">30th July &mdash; 2nd August</p>
				<p class="hero-location">Bordeaux, France</p>
			</div>

			<!-- Scroll hint -->
			<div class="scroll-hint" aria-hidden="true">
				<svg
					viewBox="0 0 24 24"
					width="20"
					height="20"
					fill="none"
					stroke="currentColor"
					stroke-width="1.5"
					stroke-linecap="round"
				>
					<path d="M7 10l5 5 5-5"></path>
				</svg>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- ============================================================
		     PERSONAL MESSAGE
		     ============================================================ -->
		<section class="content-section message-section">
			<div class="message-inner reveal-on-scroll">
				<p class="callout-text">
					FOR THE MOLE THAT <em>&ldquo;DOES NOT CARE&rdquo;</em> ABOUT HER BIRTHDAY
				</p>

				<div class="message-body">
					<p>
						As you turn 30 and obviously don't care about this &#128064; (will
						you read this, I wonder?) I thought it would be good to go somewhere
						you would not immediately guess. As you have found out, the trip is
						in Bordeaux and I'm glad you were over the moon when I told you
						about it &ldquo;?&rdquo;
					</p>
					<p>
						Maybe you even expected an agenda with the specifics but likely you
						don't expect anything at all...
					</p>
					<p class="message-standalone">
						Let's hope the early preparations were worth it.
					</p>
					<p>
						I'll take the chance to wish you a happy birthday early so that it
						is &ldquo;ticked&rdquo;, as you say. I love you lots and am grateful
						to be spending this time with you. I hope you enjoy the walks, food,
						views and fun mole times this weekend will deliver.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- ============================================================
		     QUOTE
		     ============================================================ -->
		<section class="content-section quote-section">
			<div class="section-inner reveal-on-scroll">
				<blockquote class="feature-quote">
					<p>&ldquo;Preparation leads to better outcomes&rdquo;</p>
					<cite>&mdash; Someone I agree with</cite>
				</blockquote>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- ============================================================
		     BORDEAUX INFO
		     ============================================================ -->
		<section class="content-section bordeaux-section">
			<div class="section-inner">
				<div class="section-header reveal-on-scroll">
					<span class="section-label">About the Destination</span>
					<h2 class="section-title-text">Bordeaux</h2>
				</div>

				<div class="ornamental-divider" aria-hidden="true">
					<span class="divider-line"></span>
					<span class="divider-fleuron">&#10043;</span>
					<span class="divider-line"></span>
				</div>

				<div class="bordeaux-intro reveal-on-scroll">
					<p class="bordeaux-tldr">
						<strong>TLDR:</strong> Bordeaux is an elegant, historic French city and
						UNESCO site, globally famous for its wine and stunning architecture.
					</p>
				</div>

				<div class="highlights-list reveal-on-scroll">
					<div class="highlight-item">
						<h3 class="highlight-title"><em>L'ambiance</em></h3>
						<p>Historic, sophisticated, and wine-centric.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="highlight-item">
						<h3 class="highlight-title"><em>Incontournables</em></h3>
						<p>
							The historic city centre, La Cit&eacute; du Vin museum, and the
							surrounding vineyards.
						</p>
					</div>
					<div class="highlight-item">
						<h3 class="highlight-title"><em>Les saveurs</em></h3>
						<p>
							Bordeaux wine, the local Canel&eacute;s pastry, and
							Entrec&ocirc;te &agrave; la Bordelaise.
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>

				<p class="french-slang reveal-on-scroll">
					They also have some cool French slang I have not heard in a while
					&#127467;&#127479;
				</p>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- ============================================================
		     ORDER OF EVENTS HEADER
		     ============================================================ -->
		<section class="content-section events-header-section">
			<div class="section-inner reveal-on-scroll">
				<div
					class="ornamental-divider ornamental-divider-wide"
					aria-hidden="true"
				>
					<span class="divider-line divider-line-wide"></span>
					<span class="divider-fleuron">&#10043;</span>
					<span class="divider-line divider-line-wide"></span>
				</div>
				<h2 class="events-title">Order of Events</h2>
				<p class="events-subtitle">Four days in Bordeaux &amp; beyond</p>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- ============================================================
		     DAY 1 — 30th July
		     ============================================================ -->
		<section class="day-card" id="day-1">
			<div class="day-card-inner reveal-on-scroll">
				<div class="day-header">
					<span class="day-number">30</span>
					<div>
						<span class="day-month">July</span>
						<span class="day-label">Thursday</span>
						<span class="day-theme">Arriv&eacute;e</span>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="day-rule" aria-hidden="true"></div>

				<ul class="itinerary-list">
					<li class="itinerary-item">
						<span class="item-time">Morning</span>
						<div class="item-content">
							<h3 class="item-title">Land in Bordeaux Airport at 10:00</h3>
							<p class="item-desc">Bienvenue en France.</p>
						</div>
					</li>
					<li class="itinerary-item">
						<span class="item-time">Check-in</span>
						<div class="item-content">
							<h3 class="item-title">Check in at La Maison Fernand</h3>
							<p class="item-desc">Freshen up and get ready to explore.</p>
						</div>
					</li>
					<li class="itinerary-item">
						<span class="item-time">Tick time I</span>
						<div class="item-content">
							<h3 class="item-title">Explore Old City Center</h3>
							<p class="item-desc">
								Wander the UNESCO World Heritage streets. Tick, tick, tick. We
								can say we are cultured now
							</p>
						</div>
					</li>
					<li class="itinerary-item">
						<span class="item-time">Lunch</span>
						<div class="item-content">
							<h3 class="item-title">Lunch at Les Drôles at 13h00</h3>
							<p class="item-desc">Let's start with some local flavours</p>
						</div>
					</li>
					<li class="itinerary-item">
						<span class="item-time">Tick time II</span>
						<div class="item-content">
							<h3 class="item-title">Explore Old City Center</h3>
							<p class="item-desc">Exploramoles after lunch</p>
						</div>
					</li>
					<li class="itinerary-item">
						<span class="item-time">Evening</span>
						<div class="item-content">
							<h3 class="item-title">Dinner Cruise and moley drinks</h3>
							<p class="item-note">Details:</p>
						</div>
					</li>
					<li class="itinerary-item itinerary-item-stay">
						<span class="item-time">Stay</span>
						<div class="item-content">
							<h3 class="item-title">
								<svg
									class="icon"
									viewBox="0 0 24 24"
									fill="none"
									stroke="currentColor"
									stroke-width="2"
									stroke-linecap="round"
									stroke-linejoin="round"
									aria-hidden="true"
									><path d="M5 12l-2 0l9 -9l9 9l-2 0"></path><path
										d="M5 12v7a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h10a2 2 0 0 0 2 -2v-7"></path><path
										d="M9 21v-6a2 2 0 0 1 2 -2h2a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v6"></path></svg
								>
								<a
									href="https://www.booking.com/hotel/fr/la-maison-fernand.en-gb.html"
									target="_blank"
									rel="noopener noreferrer"
									class="item-link">La Maison Fernand &nearr;</a
								>
							</h3>
						</div>
					</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- ============================================================
		     DAY 2 — 31st July
		     ============================================================ -->
		<section class="day-card day-card-adventure" id="day-2">
			<div class="day-card-inner reveal-on-scroll">
				<div class="day-header">
					<span class="day-number">31</span>
					<div>
						<span class="day-month">July</span>
						<span class="day-label">Friday</span>
						<span class="day-theme">Aventure</span>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="day-rule" aria-hidden="true"></div>

				<h3 class="day-destination">Day Trip to Arcachon</h3>

				<ul class="itinerary-list">
					<li class="itinerary-item">
						<span class="item-time">Breakfast</span>
						<div class="item-content">
							<h3 class="item-title">
								<svg
									class="icon"
									viewBox="0 0 24 24"
									fill="none"
									stroke="currentColor"
									stroke-width="2"
									stroke-linecap="round"
									stroke-linejoin="round"
									aria-hidden="true"
									><path
										d="M3 14c.83 .642 2.077 1.017 3.5 1c1.423 .017 2.67 -.358 3.5 -1c.83 -.642 2.077 -1.017 3.5 -1c1.423 -.017 2.67 .358 3.5 1"
									></path><path d="M8 3a2.4 2.4 0 0 0 -1 2a2.4 2.4 0 0 0 1 2"
									></path><path d="M12 3a2.4 2.4 0 0 0 -1 2a2.4 2.4 0 0 0 1 2"
									></path><path
										d="M3 10h14v5a6 6 0 0 1 -6 6h-2a6 6 0 0 1 -6 -6v-5"
									></path><path d="M16.746 16.726a3 3 0 1 0 .252 -5.555"
									></path></svg
								> Breakfast at La Maison Fernand
							</h3>
							<p class="item-desc">
								Last morning at our first stay before the adventure begins.
							</p>
						</div>
					</li>
					<li class="itinerary-item">
						<span class="item-time">Morning</span>
						<div class="item-content">
							<h3 class="item-title">Dune du Pilat</h3>
							<p class="item-desc">
								Europe's tallest sand dune. The views are unreal.
							</p>
						</div>
					</li>
					<li class="itinerary-item">
						<span class="item-time">Midday</span>
						<div class="item-content">
							<h3 class="item-title">Pic Niq</h3>
							<p class="item-desc">
								Merryl fromagerie, charcuterie, cave &agrave; vin et
								&eacute;picerie fine de l'aiguillon.
							</p>
						</div>
					</li>
					<li class="itinerary-item">
						<span class="item-time">Afternoon</span>
						<div class="item-content">
							<h3 class="item-title">
								Paragliding <svg
									class="icon"
									viewBox="0 0 24 24"
									fill="none"
									stroke="currentColor"
									stroke-width="2"
									stroke-linecap="round"
									stroke-linejoin="round"
									aria-hidden="true"
									><path d="M22 12a10 10 0 1 0 -20 0"></path><path
										d="M22 12c0 -1.66 -1.46 -3 -3.25 -3c-1.8 0 -3.25 1.34 -3.25 3c0 -1.66 -1.57 -3 -3.5 -3s-3.5 1.34 -3.5 3c0 -1.66 -1.46 -3 -3.25 -3c-1.8 0 -3.25 1.34 -3.25 3"
									></path><path d="M2 12l10 10l-3.5 -10"></path><path
										d="M15.5 12l-3.5 10l10 -10"></path></svg>
							</h3>
							<p class="item-desc">
								Over the dune, if we dare.
								<a
									href="https://www.pyla-parapente.com/"
									target="_blank"
									rel="noopener noreferrer"
									class="item-link"
								>
									Pyla Parapente &nearr;
								</a>
							</p>
						</div>
					</li>
					<li class="itinerary-item">
						<span class="item-time">Evening</span>
						<div class="item-content">
							<h3 class="item-title">Dinner at La Fine Bouche</h3>
						</div>
					</li>
					<li class="itinerary-item">
						<span class="item-time">Night</span>
						<div class="item-content">
							<h3 class="item-title">
								Drive to Libourne <svg
									class="icon"
									viewBox="0 0 24 24"
									fill="none"
									stroke="currentColor"
									stroke-width="2"
									stroke-linecap="round"
									stroke-linejoin="round"
									aria-hidden="true"
									><path d="M8 21l8 0"></path><path d="M12 15l0 6"></path><path
										d="M17 3l1 7c0 3.012 -2.686 5 -6 5s-6 -1.988 -6 -5l1 -7h10"
									></path><path d="M6 10a5 5 0 0 1 6 0a5 5 0 0 0 6 0"
									></path></svg>
							</h3>
							<p class="item-desc">Relaxamoles after a long day.</p>
						</div>
					</li>
					<li class="itinerary-item itinerary-item-stay">
						<span class="item-time">Check in</span>
						<div class="item-content">
							<h3 class="item-title">
								<svg
									class="icon"
									viewBox="0 0 24 24"
									fill="none"
									stroke="currentColor"
									stroke-width="2"
									stroke-linecap="round"
									stroke-linejoin="round"
									aria-hidden="true"
									><path d="M5 12l-2 0l9 -9l9 9l-2 0"></path><path
										d="M5 12v7a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h10a2 2 0 0 0 2 -2v-7"></path><path
										d="M9 21v-6a2 2 0 0 1 2 -2h2a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v6"></path></svg
								>
								<a
									href="https://www.lamaisonmulato.com/en"
									target="_blank"
									rel="noopener noreferrer"
									class="item-link">La Maison Mulato &nearr;</a
								>
							</h3>
						</div>
					</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- ============================================================
		     DAY 3 — 1st August
		     ============================================================ -->
		<section class="day-card" id="day-3">
			<div class="day-card-inner reveal-on-scroll">
				<div class="day-header">
					<span class="day-number">1</span>
					<div>
						<span class="day-month">August</span>
						<span class="day-label">Saturday</span>
						<span class="day-theme">Wine country</span>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="day-rule" aria-hidden="true"></div>

				<h3 class="day-destination">Day Trip to St. Emilion</h3>

				<ul class="itinerary-list">
					<li class="itinerary-item">
						<span class="item-time">Morning</span>
						<div class="item-content">
							<h3 class="item-title">Spa session</h3>
							<p class="item-desc">A well-deserved start to the day.</p>
						</div>
					</li>
					<li class="itinerary-item">
						<span class="item-time">Late morning</span>
						<div class="item-content">
							<h3 class="item-title">Explore Old Town</h3>
							<p class="item-desc">
								Medieval streets, limestone buildings, and endless charm.
							</p>
						</div>
					</li>
					<li class="itinerary-item">
						<span class="item-time">Midday</span>
						<div class="item-content">
							<h3 class="item-title">
								Winery Tour & Lunch <svg
									class="icon"
									viewBox="0 0 24 24"
									fill="none"
									stroke="currentColor"
									stroke-width="2"
									stroke-linecap="round"
									stroke-linejoin="round"
									aria-hidden="true"
									><path d="M8 21l8 0"></path><path d="M12 15l0 6"></path><path
										d="M17 3l1 7c0 3.012 -2.686 5 -6 5s-6 -1.988 -6 -5l1 -7h10"
									></path><path d="M6 10a5 5 0 0 1 6 0a5 5 0 0 0 6 0"
									></path></svg>
							</h3>
							<p class="item-desc">
								Taste the terroir, then a proper French lunch in the village.
							</p>
						</div>
					</li>
					<li class="itinerary-item">
						<span class="item-time">Evening</span>
						<div class="item-content">
							<h3 class="item-title">Dinner</h3>
							<p class="item-desc">Maison Mulatô dinner?</p>
						</div>
					</li>
					<li class="itinerary-item itinerary-item-stay">
						<span class="item-time">Stay</span>
						<div class="item-content">
							<h3 class="item-title">
								<svg
									class="icon"
									viewBox="0 0 24 24"
									fill="none"
									stroke="currentColor"
									stroke-width="2"
									stroke-linecap="round"
									stroke-linejoin="round"
									aria-hidden="true"
									><path d="M5 12l-2 0l9 -9l9 9l-2 0"></path><path
										d="M5 12v7a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h10a2 2 0 0 0 2 -2v-7"></path><path
										d="M9 21v-6a2 2 0 0 1 2 -2h2a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v6"></path></svg
								>
								<a
									href="https://www.lamaisonmulato.com/en"
									target="_blank"
									rel="noopener noreferrer"
									class="item-link">La Maison Mulato &nearr;</a
								>
							</h3>
						</div>
					</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- ============================================================
		     DAY 4 — 2nd August
		     ============================================================ -->
		<section class="day-card day-card-farewell" id="day-4">
			<div class="day-card-inner reveal-on-scroll">
				<div class="day-header">
					<span class="day-number">2</span>
					<div>
						<span class="day-month">August</span>
						<span class="day-label">Sunday</span>
						<span class="day-theme">Au revoir</span>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="day-rule" aria-hidden="true"></div>

				<ul class="itinerary-list">
					<li class="itinerary-item">
						<span class="item-time">Morning</span>
						<div class="item-content">
							<h3 class="item-title">Cruise Brunch</h3>
							<p class="item-desc">
								Brunch on the Garonne. A fitting farewell.
							</p>
						</div>
					</li>
					<li class="itinerary-item">
						<span class="item-time">Midday</span>
						<div class="item-content">
							<h3 class="item-title">Museum of illusions</h3>
							<p class="item-desc">One where your mole won't read everything</p>
						</div>
					</li>
					<li class="itinerary-item">
						<span class="item-time">Relax</span>
						<div class="item-content">
							<h3 class="item-title">Books & coffee</h3>
							<p class="item-desc">Gentle come down to reality</p>
						</div>
					</li>
					<li class="itinerary-item itinerary-item-stay">
						<span class="item-time">Stay</span>
						<div class="item-content">
							<h3 class="item-title">
								<svg
									class="icon"
									viewBox="0 0 24 24"
									fill="none"
									stroke="currentColor"
									stroke-width="2"
									stroke-linecap="round"
									stroke-linejoin="round"
									aria-hidden="true"
									><path d="M5 12l-2 0l9 -9l9 9l-2 0"></path><path
										d="M5 12v7a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h10a2 2 0 0 0 2 -2v-7"></path><path
										d="M9 21v-6a2 2 0 0 1 2 -2h2a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v6"></path></svg
								>
								<a
									href="https://www.lamaisonmulato.com/en"
									target="_blank"
									rel="noopener noreferrer"
									class="item-link">La Maison Mulato &nearr;</a
								>
							</h3>
						</div>
					</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- ============================================================
		     CLOSING
		     ============================================================ -->
		<section class="closing-cover" aria-label="Closing">
